flowchart TD

START((Client))--->A( creates shopping list) --> B(System calculates approximate cost<br/>Items + Rider fee + Tip)

B --> C{Wallet balance enough?}

C -- Yes --> D(Confirm delivery order)
D --> E(Reserve funds in wallet)
E --> F(Create order)
F --> G(Assign rider)
G --> H(Order confirmed → process delivery)
H --> END((End))

C -- No --> I(Show insufficient balance message)

I --> J{Client action}

J -- Top up wallet --> K(Top up wallet)
K --> B

J -- Reduce shopping list --> L(Edit shopping list)
L --> B

J -- Reduce tip --> M(Adjust tip amount)
M --> B